text: Route nationale 32 (RN 32) is a secondary highway in Madagascar from Antsohihy to Mandritsara, continuing to Andilamena. It crosses the regions of Alaotra- Mangoro and Sofia Region. ==Selected locations on route== (north to south) *Antsohihy (junction with RN 6) *Befandriana-Avaratra * river crossing *Binara *Mandritsara *Marotandrano *Ambohibary *Sahavoay *Marofano *Ambodivelatra *Antranoambo *Antanimenabaka *Andilamena (continues as RN 3a) ==See also== *List of Roads in Madagascar *Transport in Madagascar ==References== Category:Alaotra-Mangoro Category:Sofia Region Category:Roads in Madagascar
title: Route nationale 32 (Madagascar)
